Dear friends,

This is for the information of those who are interested in going on an
exchange program to TUM.

Link -
http://www.oir.iitm.ac.in/scholarship-at-technical-university-of-munich/

*Scholarship at TUM*

Technical University of Munich can provide exchange students from IIT
Madras with 1 STIBET scholarship (1,500=E2=82=AC/ student for one semester)=
.

If you want to make use of this funding opportunity, please fill out the
Nomination Form and the Letter of Approval (available on the website link
above) and send the scanned forms to oir4@wmail.iitm.ac.in or
oir4.iitm@gmail.com on or before *Tuesday,13 September 2016.*

Link to TUM Exchange =E2=80=93
http://www.international.tum.de/en/coming-to-tum/exchange-students/

